T c==> c/\ corthogonal_transformation f0 corthogonal_transformation f1 corthogonal_transformation * * part co f0 f1
D TRUTH
A |- T
T cT
D o_THM
A |- (!f. (!g. (!x. (((f o g) x) = (f (g x))))))
T c= co f0 f1 f2 * f0 * f1 f2
D LINEAR_COMPOSE
A |- (!f. (!g. (((linear f) /\ (linear g)) ==> (linear (g o f)))))
T c==> c/\ clinear f0 clinear f1 clinear * * part co f1 f0
D orthogonal_transformation
A |- (!f. ((orthogonal_transformation f) = ((linear f) /\ (!v. (!w. (((dot (f v)) (f w)) = ((dot v) w)))))))
